Package: kcorebip
Title: Bipartite networks kcore decomposition and visualization
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2025-03-31
Author: Javier Garcia-Algarra [aut, cre], Juan Manuel Garcia Santi [ctb]
Maintainer: Javier Garcia-Algarra <jgalgarra@gmail.com>
Description: Functions for k-core decomposing a bipartite graph and visualizing it with four kinds of plots: bipartite(legacy, kcoreordered and chilopodo), zigurat, matrix and polar. This package is specially suited for ecological networks.
Depends: ggplot2, rlang, grid, gridExtra, igraph, bipartite, reshape2, R (>= 4.3)
License: See LICENSE file
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
